{"id": 1672, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些现场演出的糟糕体验，让你暗下决心再也不来了？", "description": "伤心，失望，果取关。", "record_count": 10430, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170506151313A0Yjk1J9MEbmdDHa.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-08T17:00:18Z", "questions": [{"id": 2276, "title": "哪些现场演出的糟糕体验，让你暗下决心再也不来了？", "content": "哪些现场演出的糟糕体验，让你暗下决心再也不来了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 201180, "content": "买了原价/高价票，到了现场发现黄牛价只要一半", "image": "img/option/option/20170506174815ETztIGDQoaMS1WRP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201182, "content": "音乐节场地特大，舞台众多，赶场听跑得很累", "image": "img/option/option/20170506152951NYh4Cn039eQZMHIL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201184, "content": "设备故障和时间安排混乱，嘉宾耍大牌迟到", "image": "img/option/option/20170506154254hoB2RIQ15lKNixwg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201186, "content": "大多数歌手都不认识，回本的嘉宾安排在最后，想走又舍不得", "image": "img/option/option/20170506154821zfpgHAYhMxwTSGit.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201189, "content": "歌手全程跑调，但只要一敲架子鼓下面就喊“牛逼”“安可”", "image": "img/option/option/20170506173948MOBSQHn6zLqXjgZs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201190, "content": "话剧演员不专业，忘词之后瞎掰，和字幕完全对不上", "image": "img/option/option/20170506173519qImXiov6V914bCRW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201215, "content": "童年喜欢的歌手，现如今唱十场九场都车祸", "image": "img/option/option/20170506173223i1zTtwnCoLGOe4pU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201217, "content": "身边一个观众全程大声跟唱，听了一晚ta的跑调演唱会", "image": "img/option/option/201705061735020lMYdLm9xwPW1o6I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201219, "content": "前面的人一直把手机举得很高拍照摄像", "image": "img/option/option/20170506174148gPF03wpDYnbKA1Ic.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 201221, "content": "结束之后几万人一起挤地铁、打车，排队排两小时", "image": "img/option/option/20170506174558LZxG7ymYOSw8HIAc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}